Class DefaultTerm

java.lang.Object
  jason.asSyntax.DefaultTerm
All Implemented Interfaces:
Term, ToDOM, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Term>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Literal, NumberTermImpl, ObjectTermImpl, StringTermImpl
public abstract class DefaultTerm
extends java.lang.Object
implements Term, java.io.Serializable

Base class for all terms. (this class may be renamed to AbstractTerm in future releases of Jason, so avoid using it -- use ASSyntax class to create new terms)

See Also:
ASSyntax, Serialized Form
